description: Another interview with the great Carmen McRae.  This one from 1991 after a gig at the Dakota Jazz Club - in St. Paul MN at the time - in which she discusses her Thelonius Monk project, her early days in the business and the importance of the lyrics she sings.
title: Carmen McRae 1991
